<section id="about">
	<h5>About Me</h5>
	<p>I am a Research Scientist in Causality and Artificial Intelligence. After a career as a tech entrepreneur, I returned to academia to pursue a PhD at UCLA, where I worked under the guidance of <a class="link" href="https://judea.com">Judea Pearl</a>. My fascination with causal inference began when I read his book <a class="link" href="https://www.hachettebookgroup.com/titles/judea-pearl/the-book-of-why/9781541698963/">The Book of Why</a>, which sparked an enduring obsession with the principles of cause and effect. I remain deeply grateful to have studied with Dr. Pearl, whose mentorship profoundly shaped my thinking.</p>
	<p>During my PhD, I focused on personalized decision making with counterfactual reasoning. Today, my research interests have shifted toward the integration of Large Language Models and Causal Inference—exploring how causal reasoning can enhance the capabilities of LLMs, and how LLMs in turn might accelerate progress in causal discovery and reasoning. I believe this intersection will be central to advancing machine intelligence toward human-level and superhuman reasoning.</p>
	<p>Previously, I founded <a class="link" href="https://ucode.com">UCode</a>, an initiative to teach computer science to kids and teenagers. After seven years of developing approaches to make advanced concepts accessible to young students, I sought to better understand intelligence at its foundations. I believe causality lies at the heart of intelligence, reasoning, decision-making, and ultimately, the realization of <a class="link" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Artificial_general_intelligence">AGI</a>.</p>
</section>
<section id="papers">
	<h5>Papers</h5>
	<ol>
		{% for paper in papers %}
		<li>
			<p class="date">{{paper.date}}</p>
			<h6><a class="link" href="{{paper.url}}">{{paper.title}}</a></h6>
			{% if paper.publication %}
			{% if paper.publication.url %}
			<a class="title link" href="{{paper.publication.url}}">{{paper.publication.name}}</a>
			{% else %}
			<p class="title">{{paper.publication.name}}</p>
			{% endif %}
